					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Seems simple enough. You need to first find/write a ROM patch that causes music tracks in the game to be silent (trying to do this on the emulator side would be very difficult), then have the emulator watch whatever memory location the game uses to keep track of the current song playing.</div>

