						<div class="postbody">Decided to take a couple minutes and do this much for you:
<br />
<br />Megaman 2 (U):
<br /><!-- w --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.angelfire.com/nc/ugetab/Megaman2_U_Music_Remove.ips">www.angelfire.com/nc/ugetab/Megaman2_U_Music_Remove.ips</a><!-- w -->
<br />(copy and paste the link to a new window)
<br />
<br />Removes all SFX under 21, which are music. Leaves the rest intact.
<br />
<br />6502 isn't everyone's bag, even if they know a decent programming language. There's space enough to specifically make 00-20 music inits write to multiple unique addresses.</div>

					
