					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The MM2 "combo" is a LDA #music_id followed by a JSR $music_playback. I don't remeber the address, but that's it. As far as I know, there's no need of deep analysis over it. If the emulator finds the specific JSR, check the music_id and play the custom track.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><strong>Zepper</strong><br /><a href="http://rocknes.web.fc2.com/" class="postlink"><em>RockNES developer</em></a></div>
